title: I LOVE YOU Flagship Music Studio Fundraiser
desc:
This Dec 8th we honor the 44th anniversary Gang Peace Treaty which birthed the culture of Hip Hop. This will be the first of an annual event to educate the world on the true history of Hip Hop. All proceeds will support the building and launch of the Hip Hop Saves Lives flagship studio, which will serve as our home, music studio, online radio station, and online TV station from which to educate the world.? 
 
 LIVE MUSIC BY? 
 GRAND PUBA and FRIENDS, BROWN RICE FAMILY and HIP HOP SAVES LIVES YOUTH
